  "title": "Secretary",
  "description": "<p>We have an opening for the following position:</p><h3><u><strong>Legal Secretary</strong></u></h3><p><u><em>Responsibilities (not limited to):</em></u></p><ul><li>Assisting with the preparation of legal documents</li><li>Answering calls and handling requests</li><li>Scheduling of meetings/appointments and preparing of meeting materials</li><li>Maintaining client contact list</li><li>Performing general administrative duties such as photocopying, scanning, binding, file management</li><li>Providing administrative support on a day-to-day basis, such as expense claims and time recording</li><li>Preparing of billings</li><li>Booking of flights and accommodations<br /></li></ul><p><u><em>Requirements:</em></u></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 GCE \"O\" level credits including English</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft office applications</li><li>2 years' working experience as a Secretary</li><li>Takes initiative and is a team player</li><li>Excellent communication, interpersonal and organizational skill</li><li>Good time management</li></ul><p></p><p>A competitive and attractive remuneration package awaits the successful candidate.<br /></p><p>Please submit your resume stating qualifications, work experience, current and expected salary.</p><p></p>",
